Private getEdgesCompatibleWithReference

  • getEdgesCompatibleWithReference(): Edge[]
    • Defined in src/dataflow/analysis/particle-node.ts:141

    Returns the list of edges from which the given edge could have derived. The given edge must be a particle output of a Reference type. The logic behind which input/output edges could be the source of an output reference is described at go/arcs-dataflow-references.

    Returns Edge[]
